title: Blue Tuner Acorn 12x1.25 Lug Nut Kit 20 Pc Set with Key
features: Open-end blue tuner acorn lug nuts
Cold forged carbon steel with enhanced rigidity
Exceeds OEM standard in material, strength and hardness
description: Used for wheels with 60 degree tapered seating. 10 point hex opening. Bulge style helps reduce scratches against wheels. This set includes 20 pcs lug nuts and a key with 3/4" (19mm) and 13/16" (21mm) socket size. They fit most tuner type wheels which require narrow lug nut seating where regular socket cannot go in.

Style- Tuner, open-end bulge acorn type Seating- Acorn/60 degree taper Finish- Blue Material- Cold forged carbon steel Socket Key- 3/4"/19mm, 13/16"/21mm hex Overall Length- 1.27"/32mm Bulge Width- 0.75"/19mm
They do not fit wheels with mag shank type seating or radius (ball) shape seating.
